  "reference_number": "RUS1926",
  "remarks": "\nPUBLIC JOINT STOCK COMPANY “JOINT STOCK FINANCIAL CORPORATION “SYSTEM” (AFK SISTEMA) is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because: (1) it is, and has been, involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine because it makes available goods and technology that could contribute to this, namely by supplying military equipment used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation; and (2) it is, and has been, involved in obtaining a benefit from and supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian construction, defence, electronics, energy, extractives, financial services and information, communications and digital technologies sectors. \n",
